I have been "under the pump" (i.e. a huge amount of pressure) to get my business up and running in a short amount of time. Muhammad at One Design was exceptional in his responsiveness, was very considerate, patient and helpful the entire way through (I have very poor tech skills, and he was very supportive and accommodating). His skills and abilities in his work to provide what I was hoping for with the website more than met my expectations. I remain pleasantly surprised that someone who doesn't work directly in my industry grasped many of the concepts so well, and understood the core message(s) and purpose I was wanting to convey. He was very dedicated to completing the task, and did so in a thorough way and to very high standard. I would not hesitate in recommending Muhammad at One Design if you are looking for an excellent website developer who is also very pleasant and responsive to communicate with. 
Thank you for your great work!

I am beyond grateful to Muhammad. He was so patient and understanding of what I wanted for my website. He truly went above and beyond working days on end to make sure my website was as how I envisioned it. Thank you Muhammad !

One Design truly SHINES in website development! Muhammad's attention to detail and professionalism made the website build seamless, as he skillfully caught minor issues that are often overlooked. His quick responsiveness and proactive communication ensured everything was completed swiftly—HIGHLY recommend! 🤩

Very happy. Muhammad understood the brief way more than I expected someone who doesn’t work in my industry would, and went above and beyond with his services. Very professional, responsive and helpful.
I know nothing about building or doing a website, and they were so great to deal with even though I had many questions. Always fast and happy to help me.
